Sub includeFile(fSpec) With CreateObject("Scripting.FileSystemObject") executeGlobal .openTextFile(fSpec).readAll() End With End Sub

NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Checking reboot condition." Dim argCollection Set argCollection = NwEngine.DE.CommandLineArguments If argCollection.IsArgumentSupplied("SuppressReboot") Then NwEngine.Context.Reboot = 0 'Setting Flag for no Reboot NwEngine.Context.Log.WriteWarning "SAP GUI 64 Script: Reboot suppressed by the user. NwEngine.Context.Reboot = " & NwEngine.Context.Reboot ElseIf argCollection.IsArgumentSupplied("DelayReboot") Then NwEngine.Context.Reboot = 1 'Setting Flag for delayed Reboot NwEngine.Context.Log.WriteWarning "SAP GUI 64 Script: Reboot delayed by the user. NwEngine.Context.Reboot = " & NwEngine.Context.Reboot ElseIf argCollection.IsArgumentSupplied("ForceReboot") Then NwEngine.Context.Reboot = 2 'Setting Flag for immediate Reboot NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Enforce immediate reboot." End If

Else NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Key 'ShowShortcutTab' contains a customized value, leaving existing key untouched!" End If Else NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Key 'HKLM\SOFTWARE\SAP\SAPLogon' does not exist and should be created." NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue "HKLM\SOFTWARE\SAP\SAPLogon\ShowShortcutTab", "REG_DWORD", "1" End If

Option Explicit Const ForReading = 1, ForWriting = 2, ForAppending = 8 Dim jsonFileName, MHPath, strOldText, strNewText, objFSO, objFile, strText jsonFileName = NwEngine.Variables.ResolveString("%SapFrontEnd64Dir%\SAPGUI\host_manifest.json") NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI Script: host_manifest.json resolved to '" & jsonFileName & "'" MHPath = NwEngine.Variables.ResolveString("%SapFrontEnd64Dir%\SAPGUI") MHPath = Replace(MHPath, "\", "\\") strOldText = "C:\\Program Files (x86)\\SAP\\FrontEnd\\SAPgui" strNewText = MHPath Set objFSO = CreateObject("Scripting.FileSystemObject") Set objFile = objFSO.OpenTextFile(jsonFileName, ForReading) strText = objFile.ReadAll objFile.Close strNewText = Replace(strText, strOldText, strNewText) Set objFile = objFSO.OpenTextFile(jsonFileName, ForWriting) objFile.WriteLine strNewText objFile.Close

NwEngine.Shell.Use64BitHive = vbTrue NwEngine.Variables.InsertVariable "bOverWriteSAPGUIControlPlugin", "True" If NwEngine.Shell.RegKeyExist("HKLM\Software\SAP\General") Then dwSAPGUIControlPlugin = NwEngine.Shell.GetRegValue( "HKLM\Software\SAP\General\SAPGUIControlPlugin" ) NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "dwSAPGUIControlPlugin = " & dwSAPGUIControlPlugin If dwSAPGUIControlPlugin <> "" Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Do not override existing 'SAPGUIControlPlugin' key!" NwEngine.Variables.InsertVariable "bOverWriteSAPGUIControlPlugin", "False" End If End If NwEngine.Variables.Persistent("bOverWriteSAPGUIControlPlugin") = vbFalse

NwEngine.Shell.Use64BitHive = vbTrue NwEngine.Variables.InsertVariable "bOverWriteBranding", "False" If Not NwEngine.Shell.RegValueExist("HKLM\Software\SAP\General\Appearance\BrandingImage_ReadOnly") Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Value 'BrandingImage_ReadOnly' does not exist yet and is going to be written." NwEngine.Variables.AppendDefaultValue "bOverWriteBranding", "True" Else NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Do not override existing 'bOverWriteBranding' value!" End If NwEngine.Variables.Persistent("bOverWriteBranding") = vbFalse
NwEngine.Variables.InsertVariable "bOverWriteUseBranding", "False" If Not NwEngine.Shell.RegValueExist("HKLM\Software\SAP\General\Appearance\UseBrandingImage_ReadOnly") Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Value 'UseBrandingImage_ReadOnly' does not exist yet and is going to be written." NwEngine.Variables.AppendDefaultValue "bOverWriteUseBranding", "True" Else NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Do not override existing 'bOverWriteUseBranding' value!" End If NwEngine.Variables.Persistent("bOverWriteUseBranding") = vbFalse

NwEngine.Shell.Use64BitHive = vbTrue NwEngine.Variables.InsertVariable "szIEMajorVersion", "UNDEFINED" If NwEngine.Shell.RegValueExist("HKLM\Software\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\svcVersion") Then szIEVersion = NwEngine.Shell.GetRegValue ("HKLM\Software\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\svcVersion") NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Internet Explorer Version: " & szIEVersion szIEMajorVersion = Left (szIEVersion, InStr(1, szIEVersion, ".") - 1) NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Internet Explorer Major Version: " & szIEMajorVersion NwEngine.Variables.Persistent("szIEMajorVersion") = vbFalse intIEMajorVersion = CInt ( szIEMajorVersion ) ElseIf NwEngine.Shell.RegValueExist("HKLM\Software\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\Version") Then szIEVersion = NwEngine.Shell.GetRegValue ("HKLM\Software\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\Version") NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Internet Explorer Version: " & szIEVersion szIEMajorVersion = Left (szIEVersion, InStr(1, szIEVersion, ".") - 1) NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Internet Explorer Major Version: " & szIEMajorVersion NwEngine.Variables.Persistent("szIEMajorVersion") = vbFalse intIEMajorVersion = CInt ( szIEMajorVersion ) Else NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Neither registry key HKLM\Software\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\svcVersion nor Version does not exist!" End If
If ( szIEMajorVersion <> "UNDEFINED" ) Then szSapLogonFCKey = "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\MAIN\FeatureControl\FEATURE_BROWSER_EMULATION\SAPLOGON.exe" szSapLgPadFCKey = "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\MAIN\FeatureControl\FEATURE_BROWSER_EMULATION\SAPLGPAD.exe" szSapGuiFCKey = "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\MAIN\FeatureControl\FEATURE_BROWSER_EMULATION\SAPGUI.exe" szSapGuiSvFCKey = "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\MAIN\FeatureControl\FEATURE_BROWSER_EMULATION\SAPGUISERVER.exe" If ( intIEMajorVersion = 6 ) Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "No keys are going to be written for IE6." ElseIf ( intIEMajorVersion = 7 ) Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Writing keys for IE7." NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapLogonFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "8000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapLgPadFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "8000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapGuiFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "8000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapGuiSvFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "8000" ElseIf ( intIEMajorVersion = 8 ) Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Writing keys for IE8." NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapLogonFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "8000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapLgPadFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "8000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapGuiFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "8000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapGuiSvFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "8000" ElseIf ( intIEMajorVersion = 9 ) Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Writing keys for IE9." NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapLogonFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "9000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapLgPadFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "9000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapGuiFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "9000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapGuiSvFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "9000" ElseIf ( intIEMajorVersion = 10 ) Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Writing keys for IE10." NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapLogonFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "10000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapLgPadFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "10000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapGuiFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "10000" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapGuiSvFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "10000" ElseIf ( intIEMajorVersion = 11 ) Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Writing keys for IE11." NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapLogonFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "11001" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapLgPadFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "11001" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapGuiFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "11001" NwEngine.Shell.SetRegValue szSapGuiSvFCKey, "REG_DWORD", "11001" Else NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Internet Explorer Major Release not supported!!!" End If Else NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Internet Explorer not found!!!" End If

NwEngine.Shell.Use64BitHive = vbTrue szSapLogonFCKey = "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\MAIN\FeatureControl\FEATURE_BROWSER_EMULATION\SAPLOGON.exe" szSapLgPadFCKey = "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\MAIN\FeatureControl\FEATURE_BROWSER_EMULATION\SAPLGPAD.exe" szSapGuiFCKey = "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\MAIN\FeatureControl\FEATURE_BROWSER_EMULATION\SAPGUI.exe" szSapGuiSvFCKey = "HKLM\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Internet Explorer\MAIN\FeatureControl\FEATURE_BROWSER_EMULATION\SAPGUISERVER.exe" NwEngine.Shell.DeleteRegValue szSapLogonFCKey NwEngine.Shell.DeleteRegValue szSapLgPadFCKey NwEngine.Shell.DeleteRegValue szSapGuiFCKey NwEngine.Shell.DeleteRegValue szSapGuiSvFCKey

NwEngine.Shell.Use64BitHive = vbTrue szSapGui64PatchLevel = NwEngine.Variables.GetValue("SapGui64PatchLevel") NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Variable SapGui64PatchLevel has the value <" & szSapGui64PatchLevel & ">" If szSapGui64PatchLevel <> "" And szSapGui64PatchLevel <> "0" Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Checking Variable SapGui64PatchLevel: Patch found." If szSapGui64PatchLevel = "Beta" Then szGui64PatchLevelText = "Beta" Else szGui64PatchLevelText = " (" & Trim(szSapGui64PatchLevel) & ")" End If NWEngine.Variables.InsertVariable "Gui64PatchLevel", szGui64PatchLevelText Else NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SAP GUI 64 Script: Checking Variable SapGui64PatchLevel: No Patch found." NWEngine.Variables.InsertVariable "Gui64PatchLevel", "" End If

NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "Script Action: Dealing with SetSapWorkDir." lastIndex = NwEngine.Variables.GetTotalNumValues( "SetSapWorkDir" )-1 for i = 0 to lastIndex NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDir Value Number " & i & ": " & NwEngine.Variables.GetNthValue( "SetSapWorkDir", i) Next
If (lastIndex = 2) Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "The client machine already has a variable named SetSapWorkDir."
SetSapWorkDirClient = NwEngine.Variables.GetNthValue( "SetSapWorkDir", 0) SetSapWorkDirInit = NwEngine.Variables.GetNthValue( "SetSapWorkDir", 1) SetSapWorkDirPackage = NwEngine.Variables.GetNthValue( "SetSapWorkDir", 2) 'LcSetSapWorkDir = LCase(SetSapWorkDirPackage) LcSetSapWorkDir = NWEngine.Variables.ResolveString(SetSapWorkDirPackage)
NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDirInit Value: " & SetSapWorkDirInit NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDirClient Value: " & SetSapWorkDirClient NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDirPackage Value: " & SetSapWorkDirPackage
SetSapWorkDirInit = Replace (SetSapWorkDirInit, Chr(37), Chr(37) & Chr(37), 1, -1, 1) SetSapWorkDirClient = Replace (SetSapWorkDirClient, Chr(37), Chr(37) & Chr(37), 1, -1, 1) SetSapWorkDirPackage = Replace (SetSapWorkDirPackage, Chr(37), Chr(37) & Chr(37), 1, -1, 1)
NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDirInit Value Replaced: " & SetSapWorkDirInit NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDirClient Value Replaced: " & SetSapWorkDirClient NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDirPackage Value Replaced: " & SetSapWorkDirPackage
End If
If (lastIndex = 1) Then NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "The client machine doesn't have a variable named SetSapWorkDir yet."
SetSapWorkDirPackage = NwEngine.Variables.GetNthValue( "SetSapWorkDir", 0) SetSapWorkDirInit = NwEngine.Variables.GetNthValue( "SetSapWorkDir", 1) 'LcSetSapWorkDir = LCase(SetSapWorkDirPackage) LcSetSapWorkDir = NWEngine.Variables.ResolveString(SetSapWorkDirPackage)
NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDirInit Value: " & SetSapWorkDirInit NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDirPackage Value: " & SetSapWorkDirPackage
SetSapWorkDirInit = Replace (SetSapWorkDirInit, Chr(37), Chr(37) & Chr(37), 1, -1, 1) SetSapWorkDirPackage = Replace (SetSapWorkDirPackage, Chr(37), Chr(37) & Chr(37), 1, -1, 1)
NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDirInit Value Replaced: " & SetSapWorkDirInit NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDirPackage Value Replaced: " & SetSapWorkDirPackage
End If
NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "LcSetSapWorkDir Value: " & LcSetSapWorkDir
If ( SetSapWorkDirPackage <> "" ) Then NwEngine.Variables.LockVariable( "SetSapWorkDir" ) = vbFalse NwEngine.Variables.AppendDefaultValue "SetSapWorkDir", SetSapWorkDirPackage NwEngine.Context.Log.Write "SetSapWorkDir Value: " & NwEngine.Variables.GetValue ( "SetSapWorkDir" ) End If
